::Prowl::

Prowl looks into Iron Raptor's eyes, 'hearing' her wonder what she 
looked like, and projecting an image of her as well as he could, his 
love accompanying that image, as her and love had the same definition 
for him.

He also hears her thoughts about getting back to base, but then leans 
back as she does, also feeling an itching in his nose. In reality, 
there was no itching in his nose, but in his mind he was feeling what 
Iron Raptor was feeling.
